    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create legislation that stops MP's from changing parties once voted in.",
        "additional_details": "Mp's need to be held accountable for not listening to the public and need to be stopped from going against their constituency.",
        "background": "MP's should not be allowed to change to different parties once voted in by their constituency under a different party, as it can be seen as going against people democratic voice and choice.",
